wiki.summary: ANTIFRAGILE is a song recorded by South Korean girl group LE SSERAFIM. It was released on October 17, 2022 by Source Music and HYBE as the lead single of the group's second extended play of the same name. The track was written and composed by Score & Megatone of 13, Paulina 'PAU' Cerrilla, 'hitman' bang, Shintaro Yasuda, Isabella Lovestory, Kyler Niko, Ronnie Icon, Nathalia Boone and danke of lalala studio. Read more on Last.fm.
